    scene expression 'background/BG_33A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "---I'll try telling the truth."
    
    "I don't want to lie to Akiha, and if I explain everything sincerely, Akiha may understand."
    
    ".... Well, the possibility of that is like winning a lottery."
    
    "\"--Alright, let's go.\""
    
    "Taking a deep breath, I open the sitting room door."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "In the sitting room, Akiha is on the sofa and Hisui is standing by the wall."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"---Good morning, Nii-san.\""
    
    "Her gaze is telling me, \"I am angry.\""
    
    "\"Yo, morning, Akiha.\""
    
    "A defiant person is strong."
    
    "I give a cheerful greeting to Akiha's bullying gaze."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"----\""
    
    "She might be confused with my cheerfulness, as she just stares at me."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T12A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Nii-san, let's dispense with the greetings."
    
    "Please sit here; I wish to speak with you.\""
    
    "\"Sure."
    
    "Let's keep it short though.\""
    
    "I solemnly and calmly sit down on the sofa across from Akiha."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Well then, Nii-san."
    
    "This is very abrupt, but may I ask about these past two days?\""
    
    "\"-----Hm.\""
    
    ".... I knew it."
    
    "Since I left the house for two days, there's no excuse."
    
    "Time to honestly tell her all about Arcueid and these past two days."
    
    "\"About that, Akiha.\""
    
    "\"Yes, what is it, Nii-san?\""
    
    "\"These past two days, I was hunting a vampire."
    
    "You know about the recent killings, right?"
    
    "They were the work of a vampire, so I helped the 'good vampire' I met recently, and I fought with the 'bad vampire'.\""
    
    "----Like that, I explain concisely."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T15A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Wha------\""
    
    "Akiha is taken completely by surprise."
    
    ".... Well, I guess it is a natural reaction."
    
    "In her head, she's probably thinking I'm making a fool of her, and anytime in the next instant,"
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T07.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"Are you making a fool out of me, Nii-san!!!!???\""
    
    "She'll shout something like that to me--"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T10.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"..............\""
    
    "...... Huh?"
    
    "She seems upset, but she doesn't say anything."
    
    "\"Um.... Akiha?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T11A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\".... Nii-san, is this some sort of a bad joke?\""
    
    "\"------Uh..\""
    
    "Akiha looks at me quietly, like she was seeing directly into my heart."
    
    "\"No.... well, how should I put this..\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T01A.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"A joke, right?\""
    
    "\".... Well, I know it sounds like one, but..\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/AKI_T02.png' as i0 at fgpos(40, 0)
    
    "\"---No, it has to be a joke."
    
    "So please do not say such things in the future, even if it is a joke.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "She stares at me, more uneasy than angry."
    
    "Since her stare looks so serious,"
    
    "\"............ Yeah.\""
    
    "I can only nod to her."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
